@startuml separated_and_callback_tool_definitions
!pragma layout smetana
' Source evidence: cline commit c564045d8135c0c1c330b21d47b68b74917ce614, sdk/packages/shared/src/agent.ts AgentToolDefinition and AgentTool.
' Source evidence: grok-build commit 8adf9013a0929e5c7f1d4e849492d2387837a28d, xai-grok-tools tool_metadata.rs and xai-tool-runtime tool.rs.
