' Source evidence: codex commit 315195492c80fdade38e917c18f9584efd599304, codex-rs/protocol/src/dynamic_tools.rs DynamicToolFunctionSpec.
' Observed behavior: Cline and Grok split metadata from runtime, while Anthropic API and Codex route calls to a host.
' Design reason: show that a complete callable tool still needs an executor even when the descriptor is independent.
' Layout-only hidden links create a two-column grid and carry no design semantics.
